  "update_count": 70,
  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nA page can render an autofill prompt under a Picture-in-Picture (PiP) overlay. The prompt will remain open under the PiP overlay, and selecting an autofill item using the keyboard will send data to the background page. This bypasses the fix in commit 3fb0945de5e50b8e6d2f"
